I have a few dozen beater T206 and T205 cards available to trade.  My main focus is the T206 cards I don't have (want list is  [URL="http://spreadsheets.google.com/pub?key=tDUw9N8hA3ikwOFi2VqbvgA&output=html"]here[/URL]), but I will trade for pretty much any pre-war cards I don't have, I collect whatever I can get my hands on cheaply.  Beaters are a-ok by me.  

Trade list is [URL="http://spreadsheets.google.com/pub?key=ttNNzn8hw1T2sTtHp-1KLIA&output=html"]here[/URL].
Scans of the T206 cards available are [URL="http://picasaweb.google.com/tmauchter/T206Trade?authkey=Gv1sRgCILBjJb1zK3BzQE&feat=directlink"]here[/URL].
Scans of the T205 cards available are [URL="http://picasaweb.google.com/tmauchter/T205Trade?authkey=Gv1sRgCKzE7sP93vWLdQ&feat=directlink"]here[/URL].

Thanks for looking.
